profile: At Big Bear Tech, we have been providing Architectural Consulting and Design Services for a variety of clients across Western Canada for over 10 years. Our core services include consulting for Blueprints • Office/Residential layouts • Building design • Commercial and Industrial building design • Restaurant layouts • Interior Design • Finish Selection • Space Planning • 3D building design. We pride ourselves on our personalized approach and the high caliber of design for which we have become known. We believe in the value of collaboration with our Consultants, contractors and most importantly our clients.  We are truly a one-stop-shop, able to take your idea from a conception to design with the permits and approvals to get you building fast!
